117
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,500
Espere el anuncio oficial.

118
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,420
Nuestro departamento no maneja eso.

119
00:08:39,420 --> 00:08:42,310
Sí, lo siento.

120
00:08:44,730 --> 00:08:47,640
