134
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:31,410
Sí.

135
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,950
¡Muévete!

136
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:44,020
¿Están locos?

137
00:09:44,020 --> 00:09:47,160
¿Qué estaban pensando yendo allí?

138
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:50,510
